<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<%- include('../layouts/head') %>

    <body>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="container">
                <%- include('../layouts/header') %>

                    <div class="content">
                        <h1>System Logs Update</h1>
                        <p>Dear Admin,</p>

                        <p>Please find attached the logs from the last <strong>30 minutes</strong>.</p>

                        <p>This report contains detailed information regarding recent system activity. You can download
                            the attached Excel file to review the logs.</p>

                        <div class="info-box">
                            <p style="margin:0;"><strong>Report Type:</strong> System Activity Logs</p>
                            <p style="margin:0;"><strong>Generated At:</strong>
                                <%= new Date().toLocaleString() %>
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <p>If you notice anything unusual, please investigate promptly.</p>
                    </div>

                    <%- include('../layouts/footer') %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>

</html>